	STUDY <object> [#]
	LEARN <object> [#]
	 READ <object> [#]

The study command allows you to study magical scrolls and learn the 
spell that is written upon it.  Most spells have to be learned this 
way.  Once a scroll is studied, it disintegrates.  There is no
advantage to studying a similar scroll a second time. 
See help on RECITE.

You have: a grey scroll, a black scroll.
: study scroll 2
You learn the hurt spell.
The black scroll disintegrates.

